[21:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'immersed in this environment and you\'re actually on this beach during sunset. This is so realistic. And then here we have a sunlit desert. And for the most part, everything seems flawless. So really quickly, here\'s how it works. It'

[21:27] [scene:talk]
